Package org.eclipse.papyrus.arrowhead.profile.arrowheadsysmlprofile

Interface InterfaceDesignDescription

All Superinterfaces:
org.eclipse.papyrus.sysml16.blocks.Block, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.papyrus.sysml16.portsandflows.InterfaceBlock, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, ServiceDescription
All Known Implementing Classes:
InterfaceDesignDescriptionImpl
public interface InterfaceDesignDescription extends ServiceDescription
A representation of the model object 'Interface Design Description'.

The following features are supported:

  • Encoding
  • Security
  • Protocol
  • Compression
  • Crypto Algorithm
  • Token
  • Certificate Level
  • Payload Encryption
  • Time Format
